\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:452:\"<p>If you&#8217;ve been researching how to improve your content, you may have come across the idea of scannability. Scannability is powerful enough to tip the balance from online failure to success. In this article, you&#8217;ll learn about scannability and how&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/scannability/\">What is Scannability and How to Use it to Improve Content?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19688:\"<p>If you&#8217;ve been researching how to improve your content, you may have come across the idea of scannability.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Scannability is powerful enough to tip the balance from online failure to success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, you&#8217;ll learn about scannability and how to use it to achieve your website goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-scannability\">What is Scannability?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-making-pages-scannable\">Making Pages Scannable</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-does-scannability-matter\">Why Does Scannability Matter?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-when-to-make-content-scannable\">When to Make Content Scannable</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-make-your-content-scannable\">How to Make Your Content Scannable</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-improve-readability-with-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Improve Scannability With All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-scannability\">What is Scannability?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Scannability is about making it easy for people to quickly read and understand your website or text. It&#8217;s like arranging things in a way that lets them easily skim through and get the main points without much effort.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The term scannability became popular after a <a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/how-users-read-on-the-web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">fascinating study</a> was published by the Nielsen Norman Group in 1997.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Researcher Jakob Nielsen and his team sought to discover how users read on the web.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Their conclusion? &#8220;They don&#8217;t.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;People rarely read Web pages word by word; instead, they <strong>scan</strong> the page, picking out individual words and sentences.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Only a small minority of users in the study read pages word-for-word.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Subsequent research came to the same conclusion.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-making-pages-scannable\">Making Pages Scannable</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nielsen&#8217;s team developed simple guidelines for making pages <strong>scannable</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The goal? <em>Write</em> to help people <em>scan</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These guidelines include using short paragraphs, subheadings, and putting the most important information at the <em>beginning </em>of a page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a page to be scannable, the <em>formatting must match how users read online</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the years since the original study, scannability became a key feature of high-performing content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"418\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-1024x418.jpg\" alt=\"example of scannability\" class=\"wp-image-271116\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-1024x418.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-300x122.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-768x313.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-1536x627.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-2048x836.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-600x245.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-147x60.jpg 147w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/scannable-content-example-221x90.jpg 221w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>This summary helps users decide quickly whether this page is helpful for them. They can immediately opt to explore 2 related topics. (Source:</em><a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/layer-cake-pattern-scanning/\"> <em>NN/g</em></a><em>)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-why-does-scannability-matter\">Why Does Scannability Matter?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Scannability matters because it impacts engagement, conversions, and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A user will decide whether to leave or stay on a web page within a few seconds.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A scannable page helps a user determine if the content meets his needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For these reasons, scannability is essential for successful content marketing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-when-to-make-content-scannable\">When to Make Content Scannable</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While scannability will improve most web content, there are some cases where it wouldn&#8217;t be appropriate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, narrative nonfiction journalism or literature attracts users who want to read word-for-word. And putting the conclusion at the beginning of a novel wouldn&#8217;t make sense.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, even some of this content may benefit from being formatted for easier screen reading.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, editors of the captivating &#8220;<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/projects/2012/snow-fall/index.html#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Snow Fall</a>&#8221; story broke up the long text with short chapter subheadings, video interviews with witnesses, animated graphics, and photos.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These orient and engage the reader.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"521\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-1024x521.jpg\" alt=\"new york times snowfall article\" class=\"wp-image-271103\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-1024x521.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-300x153.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-768x391.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-600x305.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-118x60.jpg 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt-177x90.jpg 177w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/new-york-times-snowfall-excerpt.jpg 1126w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-make-your-content-scannable\">How to Make Your Content Scannable</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow these simple guidelines to make your web pages scannable.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-above-the-fold-considerations\">Above-the-Fold Considerations</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Above-the-fold refers to the portion of a web page that&#8217;s visible without scrolling down.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most users will decide within seconds whether to stay on the page, leave, or click on a link. So, what&#8217;s at the top of a page matters.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Inverted Pyramid</strong>: The Nielsen Norman Group (NN/g) recommends putting your <em>conclusion</em> and most important information at the beginning of your page.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Key Links</strong>: Consider moving the page&#8217;s most important link(s) to the top. Keep those links to a minimum to avoid presenting too many options.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/adding-breadcrumbs-to-your-site-using-the-aioseo-breadcrumbs-block/\"><strong>Breadcrumbs</strong></a>: These tiny navigation links don&#8217;t take up much room. And they can entice readers who decide not to scroll further.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Category Tags</strong>: Place these at the top to engage users who decide not to remain on the page.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-inverted-pyramid-to-improve-web-content/\" title=\"\">inverted pyramid approach</a> is copied from news writing. Journalists often place the &#8220;5W and H&#8221; at the beginning: Who, What, How, When, Where, and Why. Details follow.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-below-the-fold\">Below the Fold</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Subheadings: </strong>Break up walls of text with short, descriptive subheadings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Short paragraphs</strong>: Limit paragraph size to &#8220;<a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/how-users-read-on-the-web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">one idea</a>.&#8221;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Lists</strong>: Vary your formatting by using numbered or bulleted lists where useful.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bolded text or Italics</strong>: Highlight keywords, but use this technique sparingly.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Stylized Pull Quotes</strong>: With an eye-catching design, short pull quotes can boost scannability. Consider highlighting what&#8217;s unusual or surprising.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Highlight Asides</strong>: Consider visually highlighting sidebar text to differentiate it from the main flow of the article.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Images and Screengrabs</strong>: These can be useful for breaking up long stretches of text, but images should only be used if they are helpful to the reader. Be cautious when using<a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/videos/decorative-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"> decorative images</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Visual Data Representation</strong>: Where helpful to the reader, present data visually in charts, tables, or interactive data embeds.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-improve-readability-with-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Improve Scannability With All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To put these ideas into practice, we recommend using <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin analyzes your pages for readability and scannability <em>in addition to SEO</em>. These readability and SEO checks include instructions on what to change.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s how the readability feature works. AIOSEO checks:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Paragraph length</strong>: The target is no more than 120 words per paragraph. Longer passages are difficult for users to read on screens.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Images/videos</strong> in content: If there are none, you&#8217;ll be encouraged to add <em>relevant</em> media.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sentence length</strong>: AIOSEO checks for excessive sentence length. The target word count is 20.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Subheading distribution</strong>: The plugin checks to ensure you&#8217;re breaking up content with subheadings. It will suggest adding subheads to passages longer than 300 words.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-flesch-reading-ease-score-to-grow-traffic/\" title=\"\">Flesch Reading Ease</a></strong>: The plugin uses the Flesch-Kincaid readability tests to assess how easy it is to read your content. You&#8217;ll see recommended improvements.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once youve installed the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin, log in to any WordPress page to get these recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your All in One SEO tools will appear to the right of your article.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on <strong>Readability,</strong> and you&#8217;ll get suggestions for improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability.png\" alt=\"aioseo readability\" class=\"wp-image-248393\" style=\"width:352px;height:261px\" width=\"352\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability.png 698w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-300x222.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-600x444.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-81x60.png 81w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-122x90.png 122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 352px) 100vw, 352px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-548x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-271167\" style=\"width:355px;height:663px\" width=\"355\" height=\"663\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-548x1024.png 548w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-160x300.png 160w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-768x1436.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-600x1122.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-32x60.png 32w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2-48x90.png 48w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-items-to-fix-truseo-highlighter-2.png 790w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 355px) 100vw, 355px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll also see what doesn&#8217;t need improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items.png\" alt=\"aioseo readability good items\" class=\"wp-image-271109\" style=\"width:362px;height:298px\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items.png 936w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items-300x247.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items-768x633.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items-600x494.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items-73x60.png 73w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/aioseo-readability-good-items-109x90.png 109w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 362px) 100vw, 362px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO is an established plugin with thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org. Over 3 million people are using the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing starts at <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">$49.50/year</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-moving-forward-with-scannability\">Moving Forward With Scannability</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Research shows that when you write with scannability in mind, your content will be easier for users to consume.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good formatting allows for more white space around page elements, and this is easier on the readers eye.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These principles work not only for desktop or mobile screen apps but also for user interfaces and web design overall.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Curious readers may want to delve into the Nielsen Norman Groups eye-tracking studies and research into reading/scanning patterns, such as the <a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/f-shaped-pattern-reading-web-content/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">f-pattern</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Youll find valuable insights to apply to your website and content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Nielsen Norman Group is considered one of the worlds premier user experience (UX) design consultancies. Their blog highlights findings and applications of their usability testing and user research.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-bonus-tip-lead-capture\">Bonus Tip: Lead Capture</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Scannable content will engage more readers, but youll still have some who want to leave quickly. This is where an <strong>exit-intent pop-up</strong> is useful.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These pop-ups will appear when people are <em>leaving</em> your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We use the OptinMonster plugin for our exit-intent pop-ups and found it to be a reliable way to boost conversions and revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Youll get a beginner-friendly way to create pro-looking call-to-action designs. And the plugin is<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"> low-cost</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Browse this <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/exit-intent-popup-examples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">gallery</a> of examples and check out the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">results from users</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-271112\" style=\"width:467px;height:273px\" width=\"467\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example.png 781w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example-300x176.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example-768x449.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example-600x351.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/optinmonster-popup-example-154x90.png 154w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>The OptinMonster gallery features their customers popups.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Breadcrumbs</strong>: You can<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/adding-breadcrumbs-to-your-site-using-the-aioseo-breadcrumbs-block/\"> add breadcrumbs</a> with a click of a button with the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What&#8217;s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you understand what scannability is and how you can use it to create better content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-copywriting/\">copywriting tips</a> and tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">writing meta-descriptions for SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>, where we publish new tutorials weekly. And join us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/scannability/\">What is Scannability and How to Use it to Improve Content?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://aioseo.com/scannability/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"Introducing the Author SEO (Google E-E-A-T) Addon in AIOSEO 4.5.4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:150:\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:30:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"author seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"google eeat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=268289\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:458:\"<p>Were so excited to start the year off with one of the most exciting updates to our plugin. Introducing the Author SEO addon in AIOSEO 4.5.4. This is a powerful module that will help you meet Googles E-E-A-T content guidelines,&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon/\">Introducing the Author SEO (Google E-E-A-T) Addon in AIOSEO 4.5.4</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14137:\"<p>Were so excited to start the year off with one of the most exciting updates to our plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Introducing the Author SEO addon in AIOSEO 4.5.4.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a powerful module that will help you meet Googles E-E-A-T content guidelines, resulting in better rankings and increased traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-google-e-e-a-t\">What is Google E-E-A-T?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-implementing-google-e-e-a-t-has-become-easier-with-aioseo-4-5-4\">Implementing Google E-E-A-T Has Become Easier with AIOSEO 4.5.4</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-leverage-your-author-bio\">Leverage Your Author Bio</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-boost-authority-and-credibility-by-adding-a-reviewer\">Boost Authority and Credibility by Adding a Reviewer</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-implementing-author-seo-with-shortcodes\">Implementing Author SEO with Shortcodes</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Announcing The Google E-E-A-T Addon For AIOSEO\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vkMJUBtQdho?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-google-e-e-a-t\">What is Google E-E-A-T?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-google-eat/\" title=\"What is Google E-E-A-T?  Understanding Googles Secret Sauce for Creating Effective Content\">Google&#8217;s E-E-A-T</a> stands for Expertise, Experience, Authoritativeness, and Trustworthiness. It is a set of criteria that Google uses to assess the quality of content on the web, particularly for pages that deal with topics related to health, finance, and other areas where accuracy and reliability are crucial.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The concept is prominently mentioned in Google&#8217;s Search Quality Evaluator Guidelines, which are guidelines given to human evaluators who assess the quality of search results. Google designed these to ensure the content published online is of high quality. E-E-A-T is an acronym that stands for:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Experience</strong>: refers to the first-hand experiences the author or other members of the team have with that particular topic.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Expertise</strong>: refers to the expertise of the creator of the main content.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Authoritativeness</strong>: refers to the authoritativeness of the main content creator, the content, and the website the content is published on.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Trustworthiness</strong>: Refers to the trustworthiness of the main content creator, the content itself, and the website its published on.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The purpose of these standards is to help improve the quality of content published on the web. In addition, it helps ensure that content is accurate and helpful to users. This has become even more critical since the rollout of the Helpful Content Update (HCU).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-implementing-google-e-e-a-t-has-become-easier-with-aioseo-4-5-4\">Implementing Google E-E-A-T Has Become Easier with AIOSEO 4.5.4</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With AIOSEO 4.5.4, its now easier to showcase E-E-A-T signals on your posts and pages, thanks to the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/author-seo-google-e-e-a-t/\" title=\"Author SEO  Google E-E-A-T Addon\">Author SEO addon</a>. You can now specify your areas of expertise, your experience, and more. You can do that in the <strong>Users</strong> section of your WordPress Dashboard. If you update to AIOSEO 4.5.4, youll find a new section called <strong>Author SEO</strong>, where you can input information to boost your E-E-A-T SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"403\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/edit-user.png\" alt=\"Author SEO tab.\" class=\"wp-image-268292\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/edit-user.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/edit-user-300x173.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/edit-user-600x345.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Author SEO section is where you can add an authors information to help validate your E-E-A-T signals.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"496\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-1.png\" alt=\"Toggle to enable Author Info fields.\" class=\"wp-image-268293\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-1-300x212.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-1-600x424.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the author info you can add include</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Alumni Of</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Employer</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Job Title</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And because AIOSEO outputs JSON schema for said information, search engines can easily understand it and take it into consideration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides your credentials and role in your organization, you can also add categories of your areas of expertise.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"238\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/knows-about-section.png\" alt=\"&quot;Knows About&quot; section in the Author Info  section.\" class=\"wp-image-268294\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/knows-about-section.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/knows-about-section-300x102.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/knows-about-section-600x203.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All this information points to your experience and expertise in your field. Plus, coupled with the JSON schema markup, it proves to search engines that youre qualified to talk about the subject. This helps you rank higher in searches around your keyword.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-leverage-your-author-bio\">Leverage Your Author Bio</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Trust is one of the key pillars in Googles E-E-A-T content guidelines. One way you can gain readers trust is by letting them know who you are. This is why we added some blocks to help you inject author information into your posts. To get started, fill in your author bio information in the Author SEO section:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-2.png\" alt=\"Author Bio fields\" class=\"wp-image-268295\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-2.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-2-300x236.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-info-2-600x472.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The author bio section allows you to add your author image, an author excerpt, and a full author bio.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One way of leveraging your bio is by adding an Author Name (Written By) author block. This gives a very brief summary of the posts author. Hovering over the author&#8217;s name reveals a tooltip with a mini bio.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"408\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-tooltip.png\" alt=\"Author bio tooltip\" class=\"wp-image-268296\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-tooltip.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-tooltip-300x174.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-tooltip-600x349.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also add an author bio at the bottom of your page. By default, this will be a compact bio.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"388\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/eeat-bio-example.png\" alt=\"Compact bio\" class=\"wp-image-268297\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/eeat-bio-example.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/eeat-bio-example-300x166.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/eeat-bio-example-600x332.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This gives a brief summary of the author. It also:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Links to the author&#8217;s archive page (page with all the authors articles)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Showcases your areas of expertise</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Links to your social media accounts</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You can choose to display the full bio by going to the Author Bio block settings and turning the <strong>Show Compact Author Bio</strong> toggle off.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/compact-bio-toggle.png\" alt=\"Show Compact Author Bio toggle.\" class=\"wp-image-268298\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/compact-bio-toggle.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/compact-bio-toggle-300x255.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/compact-bio-toggle-600x510.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This results in your full bio being displayed:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"684\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-2-1.png\" alt=\"Full bio example\" class=\"wp-image-268291\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-2-1.png 684w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-2-1-300x292.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/author-bio-2-1-600x584.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 684px) 100vw, 684px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, this helps you demonstrate your expertise, experience, authority, and trustworthiness. As a result, meeting Googles E-E-A-T guidelines is easier.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-boost-authority-and-credibility-by-adding-a-reviewer\">Boost Authority and Credibility by Adding a Reviewer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great way to boost your credibility is by adding a reviewer for your content. This helps show that your content has been fact-checked and is accurate. Thats why we added support for showcasing a reviewer on your posts.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"399\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/reviewer-block.png\" alt=\"Reviewer block\" class=\"wp-image-268299\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/reviewer-block.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/reviewer-block-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/reviewer-block-600x341.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is particularly important for YMYL articles, where you need to demonstrate that your content is accurate, up-to-date, and reliable. A reviewer also shows that your content is backed up by an expert and can be trusted.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding a reviewer goes a long way in helping you build trust and authority, boosting your Google E-E-A-T score.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-implementing-author-seo-with-shortcodes\">Implementing Author SEO with Shortcodes</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides the blocks, AIOSEOs Author SEO addon also supports shortcodes and PHP functions. Some of the shortcodes the addon supports include:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&#91;aioseo_eeat_author_tooltip show-label=\"true\" show-image=\"true\" show-tooltip=\"true\"]\n\n&#91;aioseo_eeat_reviewer_tooltip show-label=\"true\" show-image=\"true\" show-tooltip=\"true\"]\n\n&#91;aioseo_eeat_author_bio compact=\"false\"]</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Supported PHP functions include:</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>aioseo_eeat_author_tooltip( $showLabel = true, $showImage = true, $showTooltip = $true );\n\naioseo_eeat_reviewer_tooltip( $showLabel = true, $showImage = true, $showTooltip = true );\n\naioseo_eeat_author_bio( $compact = true )</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>These shortcodes and PHP functions make it easier to embed Author SEO elements anywhere on a post or page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides the E-E-A-T addon, weve also made improvements to other features you already know and love. You can see all our changes in our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/changelog/\">full product changelog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Update your site to AIOSEO 4.5.4 to unlock these powerful new features and rank your content higher on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if youre not yet using AIOSEO, make sure to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">install and activate the plugin today</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have questions about these features, please comment below or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact Us\">contact our customer support team</a>. Were always ready to help. Our commitment to making AIOSEO the easiest and best WordPress SEO plugin is only getting stronger as we continue to win together with our customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Were so grateful for your continued support, feedback, and suggestions. Please keep those suggestions and feature requests coming!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoy using these new SEO features as much as we enjoyed creating them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>-Benjamin Rojas (President of AIOSEO).</em></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon/\">Introducing the Author SEO (Google E-E-A-T) Addon in AIOSEO 4.5.4</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-author-seo-google-e-e-a-t-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\